    narr:narration """This hub collects Aswritten's load-bearing key phrases and voice/style observations — the recognition surface for how the company names itself. The founding positioning cluster runs through [narrative as steering vector](narr:Obs_KeyPhrase_SteeringVector), [worldview as code](narr:Obs_KeyPhrase_WorldviewAsCode), [underneath the text](narr:Obs_KeyPhrase_UnderneathTheText), [think like your org](narr:Obs_KeyPhrase_ThinkLikeYourOrg), and the [attention-dilution-vs-steering differentiator](narr:Obs_KeyPhrase_AttentionDilution). Buyer-facing stock phrases include [institutional knowledge at the cursor](narr:StyleObs_StockPhrase_InstitutionalKnowledge), [senior expert bottleneck](narr:StyleObs_StockPhrase_SeniorExpertBottleneck), [collective memory](narr:StyleObs_CollectiveMemory), and the [where-you've-been tricolon](narr:StyleObs_RuleOfThree_Direction). Voice-level observations document Scarlet's idiolect: [archery/arrow metaphors](narr:StyleObs_5), [worldview-as-installable-program](narr:StyleObs_Metaphor_InstallableProgram), [Clojure-framed architecture](narr:StyleObs_ClojureIdiolect), [lowercase brand stylization](narr:StyleObs_BrandNameStylization), antithesis/reframe constructions ([not-X-it's-Y](narr:StyleObs_VerbatimReframe)), and conviction-labeled meta-transparency. Coined product terms ([lens drafting](narr:StyleObs_LensDraftingTerm), [micro-telltale](narr:StyleObs_LensMicroTelltale), [collective memory](narr:Observation_KeyPhrases_1)) recur. The opening hook itself shifts over time — from enterprise framing toward [the hallucination question](narr:Obs_KeyPhrase_Hallucinating) and [context engineering](narr:Obs_KeyPhrase_ContextEngineering) as the reframe.""" ;
